---
title: Nutty Crusted Chicken with Crispy Potatoes and Tenderstem
description: Although walnuts and rosemary are delicious individually, together they're an absolute winner! This herby chicken isn’t just delicious though, it's good for you too. Walnuts are full of omega-3 which is great for brain health and researchers have also recently discovered that rosemary helps with memory. You could say this dish is food for thought!
